{
  "text": "Animals had previously seen a coiled snake [CITATION_1] , that was similar to the one used in this experiment but significantly smaller in size. All other objects were novel to the animals. Additionally, animals had no previous experience with other living mammals (with the exception of their human caretakers and experimenters) or reptiles because they were born, raised and housed indoors.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "4846674"
